  • Easy Operation: The plug-and-play remote control outlet is pre-paired and requires no wiring. Its user-friendly remote includes push buttons to switch each socket on and off independently. This considerate and useful feature is particularly ideal for the elderly or those with physical limitations
  • Strong Signal: With a reliable range of up to 100 feet and a strong signal that goes through walls, the wireless remote control lets you effortlessly control your devices from any room in your home. Even with multiple devices, its frequency remains unaffected, ensuring excellent performance and stability, enhancing your smart living experience
  • Programmable and Expandable: WILAWELS remote control socket kit is expandable with extra remotes, sockets or lamp bases of the same brand. The pairing process simplifies the control of multiple sockets with a single remote or a device with multiple remotes, giving you the freedom to customize your lighting combination
  • Versatile Solution: The smart and convenient remote control light switch kit is suitable for various settings. It displays its versatility by remotely controlling a variety of household appliances, such as lamps, fans, chargers, air conditioners, stereos and heaters from anywhere in your home to meet your diverse needs
  • Safety and Energy Savings: The remote control outlet kit is made of flame-retardant PC material and is certified by the FCC for quality assurance. This kit comes with 1 remote control (a 23A battery included) and 1 socket that can support up to 1875W/15A/125V. By using this kit, you can ensure a secure and energy-efficient smart home experience
